{"tid":973558,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"三星夥蘋果　電視支援iTunes 及AirPlay","createTime":"2019-01-08T09:07:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-08T13:23:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f3e531a0063299c6ed0fedcae7602e8b94058624","tid":973558,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T09:07:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190108/20586014\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190108%2F20586014&d=4Ag1gy5rOgZ5EjT6Eq90HDM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=9d61699d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190108%2F20586014&h=9d425878\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190108/20586014</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年01月08日 <br />\n<br />\n三星夥蘋果　電視支援iTunes 及AirPlay<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190108/large/a1503a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190108%2Flarge%2Fa1503a.gif&h=d160aa53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在手機市場惡鬥多年的南韓三星集團和美國蘋果「化敵為友」，三星旗下電視機將可裝設蘋果iTunes網上影音內容（圖），顯示一向「獨食」的蘋果策略有變，與對手合作增加營利。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新iPhone用三星OLED減磅<br />\n<br />\n年度電子展CES於美國賭城舉行前兩天，三星公佈春天起出產的智能電視將新增程式供用戶下載iTunes電影與劇集，並支援蘋果串流技術AirPlay 2，以播放蘋果產品的內容。相關程式在逾100個國家發售的三星智能電視提供；去年售出的智能電視，將為190國客戶提供系統升級，以支援上述兩項蘋果功能。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果互聯網軟件和服務部副總裁庫埃亦發聲明：「我們樂見全球更多顧客能藉着三星智能電視體驗iTunes和AirPlay 2，亦讓iPhone、iPad和Mac電腦用戶可用另一種方式，安坐家中以大螢幕觀賞心水內容。」三星表示，蘋果影音服務用戶眾多，在旗下智能電視產品上加入上述功能，可吸引蘋果用戶使用他們產品；市場上最大的4K HDR 影片資料庫iTunes同時成為集團囊中物。<br />\n<br />\n另外，據報蘋果新一批iPhone，亦將使用三星OLED輕觸螢幕技術，為笨重的手機設計「減磅」。<br />\n<br />\n美國有線新聞網絡  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n國安顧問：美殲滅IS前不會撤出敍北<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n空襲也門阿蓋德　 美殺18年前炸艦主謀"},{"pid":"c5465e93909c17d0384db84e1d4d640b3ae1a89e","tid":973558,"uid":16404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T09:22:27.000Z","msg":"搞cheap晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37909f50005317f8e86123c7627ee4c57098720e","tid":973558,"uid":45368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T10:42:58.000Z","msg":"apple 自甘墮落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95609a0994e172050c98830ed76301e9afbc4524","tid":973558,"uid":31098,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T10:51:06.000Z","msg":"添曲為錢真係可以連原則都唔要喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2570097274acd9a49cd7ebf1a43da0cd8775d148","tid":973558,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T13:10:30.000Z","msg":"好正播，以前徧向日本電視，睇黎下一部要睇下韓國機。"},{"pid":"8f2244997a9e71b1e6afd2a59db11f8e00c8cf15","tid":973558,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T13:16:35.000Z","msg":"蘋果唔會自己出電視嘢話<br />\n呢步係好旗嚟<br />\n聯手對付d 鬼國牌/ 貼牌鬼國機"},{"pid":"2791ba7980e70b2b032fa01eda980163c694497c","tid":973558,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f2244997a9e71b1e6afd2a59db11f8e00c8cf15","tid":973558,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T13:16:35.000Z","msg":"蘋果唔會自己出電視嘢話<br />\n呢步係好旗嚟<br />\n聯手對付d 鬼國牌/ 貼牌鬼國機"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T13:16:51.000Z","msg":"*棋"},{"pid":"634a94b0620e7107e55e595540bedc026da5a65a","tid":973558,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2791ba7980e70b2b032fa01eda980163c694497c","tid":973558,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f2244997a9e71b1e6afd2a59db11f8e00c8cf15","tid":973558,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T13:16:35.000Z","msg":"蘋果唔會自己出電視嘢話<br />\n呢步係好旗嚟<br />\n聯手對付d 鬼國牌/ 貼牌鬼國機"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T13:16:51.000Z","msg":"*棋"},"cit